divs: Sighting DetailsWhile out on my balcony at 7:40PM (Oct. 24, 2008), I noticed several ORB shaped objects moving in various directions in the West view. I took 2 pictures of them, and then they were gone. No noise, no bright lights, no exhaust trails.... they looked almost translucent, or pale. MAGNIFY my "yellow-highlighted" circles on the 2 photos to view them!
Summary: More ORB shaped objects above the London Ontario (Canada) skies.
